_sText:
This is (another) remake of surf_leet
It has a jail with a keypad and a free Button.
The Code for the jail trap is: 1389
You can open the jail and free the people in it by pressing the empty red button.
Theres also a fully working nuke in the jail which you can activate either by inputting a secret keypad code an youll survive or you throw a grenade to the nuke which will instakill you and everyone else in jail.
Pls comment much on this release.
Picture 3 shows the nuke after it exploded.
Have much fun with this map.
Oh and I need a studio so if someone is interested pls contact me :D

PS: There is a bug that prevents MODTD from working...just press Enter a few times and youll start. Blame Valve for that :)
